      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "SURVIVAL RULES\r\n\u25BA Your health drains constantly \u2014 work fast!\r\n\u25BA 
    The ghost CHASES you when your lantern is ON\r\n\u25BA Turn lantern OFF to hide
    from the ghost\r\n\u25BA  You can only interact with objects when lantern is
    ON\r\n\u25BA  The ghost KILLS you if it gets too close\r\n\u25BA  Find pill boxes
    near unlocked doors to restore health\r\r\n"
