  m_text: "YARD\r\n  \u25BA Repair the fuse box \u2014 remember the sequence!\r\n 
    \u25BA Consult the Ouija Board \u2014 choose your answers wisely\r\n  \u25BA
    Test your timing \u2014 stop the ball in the green zone\r\n  \u25BA Collect all
    8 horror dolls and burn them at the bonfire\r\n\r\nUNLOCKS\r\nComplete 2 tasks 
    \u2192 Hall door unlocks + Health pill appears\r\nComplete 4 tasks  \u2192 Yard
    door unlocks + Health pill appears\r\nComplete 8 tasks  \u2192 Exit gate unlocks
    \u2014 ESCAPE!\r\n"
